. Scilab is now case sensitive and identifiers may be up to 24 character long
  check for your own scilab-1 version macros files for unwanted different upper
  and lower case identifiers

. Many changes have been done on the major scilab window, help and graphics

. Geci

. New functions
  plot3di, unix_s, unix_g, unix_x, xgetmouse, 

